    'No calls for chapters are currently open. Panorama Research Institute\'s edited volume program is in its planning stage, with the first volume anticipated to be announced in 2026.': '当前暂无开放的章节征集。全景研究院主编文集项目处于规划阶段，首部文集预计于 2026 年公布。',
    'If you are interested in proposing an edited volume, please see the': '如有意提出主编文集提案，请参阅',
    'edited volume proposal': '主编文集提案',
    'page.': '页面。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is developing a program of edited academic volumes on themes central to its research program. Edited volumes bring together original chapters from multiple scholars, providing a comprehensive treatment of a research theme that no single author could produce alone.': '全景研究院正在围绕其研究项目核心主题发展主编学术文集项目。主编文集汇集多位学者的原创章节，对单一作者难以独立完成的研究主题进行综合讨论。',
    'When a call for chapters is open, chapter contributors do not need to be formally affiliated with the Institute. Submissions must fall within the scope of the volume, meet the Institute\'s publication standards, and be submitted by the stated deadline. Each call includes specific guidance on the expected chapter length, format, review process, and publication timeline.': '开放章节征集时，章节作者不必正式隶属于研究院。投稿必须符合文集范围，达到研究院出版标准，并在规定截止日期前提交。每项征集都会说明章节预期长度、格式、评审流程和出版时间表。',
    'Planned Volumes': '规划中的文集',
    'Scholarly Publishing ? 2026 (planned)': '学术出版 2026（计划中）',
    'Open Access and Scholarly Communication in Asia-Pacific': '亚太地区开放获取与学术传播',
    'Scholarly Indexing and Evaluation ? 2026 (planned)': '学术索引与评价 2026（计划中）',
    'Journal Evaluation Beyond the Impact Factor: Alternative Frameworks and Approaches': '超越影响因子的期刊评价：替代框架与方法',
    'Open calls for paper and abstract submissions for conferences, seminars, and other events organized or co-organized by Panorama Research Institute.': '全景研究院主办或联合主办会议、研讨会及其他活动的论文和摘要征集。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is currently in its foundational phase. No calls for papers are currently open. Calls for papers will be published here and distributed via the Institute\'s mailing list when announced.': '全景研究院目前处于基础建设阶段。当前暂无开放论文征稿。征稿发布后将在此公布，并通过研究院邮件列表发送。',
    'The Institute\'s first major conference is planned for 2026. Calls for papers will be issued approximately six months before the event.': '研究院首个大型会议计划于 2026 年举行。论文征稿预计将在活动前约六个月发布。',
    'How Calls Work': '征集流程',
    'When a call for papers is open, it will be listed here with the event name, submission deadline, format requirements, themes, and submission link. Submissions may be for full papers, extended abstracts, or panel proposals, depending on the event.': '开放论文征稿时，本页将列出活动名称、投稿截止日期、格式要求、主题和提交链接。根据活动类型，投稿可包括全文论文、扩展摘要或专题小组提案。',
    'All submissions are reviewed by the event\'s scientific committee. Accepted papers will be notified and invited to present. Selected presentations from Institute-organized conferences and seminars may be developed into publications in the Institute\'s working paper or other series.': '所有投稿均由活动学术委员会评审。被接受论文的作者将收到通知并受邀报告。研究院主办会议和研讨会中的部分报告可进一步发展为研究院工作论文或其他系列出版成果。',
    'Planned Future Calls': '未来计划征集',
