    'Panorama Research Seminar Series — Inaugural Session': '全景研究研讨会系列——首场活动',
    '2026 (planned)': '2026 年（计划中）',
    'Workshop Proposals': '工作坊提案',
    'First Workshop on Journal Evaluation and Indexing': '首届期刊评价与索引工作坊',
    'Academic conferences organized and co-organized by Panorama Research Institute, bringing together scholars, policymakers, and practitioners in the Institute\'s research areas.': '全景研究院主办和联合主办的学术会议，汇集研究院相关领域的学者、政策制定者和实践者。',
    'Panorama Research Institute plans to develop an international conference program centered on the Institute\'s core research themes of scholarly publishing, journal evaluation, academic policy, and emerging digital futures. The first Institute-organized conference is planned for 2026.': '全景研究院计划发展国际会议项目，围绕学术出版、期刊评价、学术政策和新兴数字未来等核心研究主题展开。研究院首个主办会议计划于 2026 年举行。',
    'Upcoming — Planning Stage': '即将开展——规划阶段',
    'The Institute is in the early planning stage for its inaugural international conference on scholarly communication, academic publishing, and open science. The conference will bring together researchers, editors, publishers, librarians, and policymakers from across the Asia-Pacific region and beyond.': '研究院首届关于学术传播、学术出版和开放科学的国际会议处于早期规划阶段。会议将汇集亚太地区及其他地区的研究人员、编辑、出版商、图书馆员和政策制定者。',
