    'Co-organize a Conference': '联合主办会议',
    'Events &amp; Calls': '活动与征集',
    'Annual Conference on Scholarly Publishing Studies': '学术出版研究年度会议',
    'Edited Volume: The Future of Scholarly Publishing': '主编文集：学术出版的未来',
    'Policy and Social Research Seminar Series': '政策与社会研究研讨会系列',
    'The Institute offers training workshops and programs for researchers, journal editors, and academic professionals in areas including scholarly publishing, research methodology, peer review, and publication ethics.': '研究院为研究人员、期刊编辑和学术专业人员提供培训工作坊和项目，领域包括学术出版、研究方法、同行评审和出版伦理。',
    'Academic Seminars': '学术研讨会',
    'Academic seminars organized by Panorama Research Institute, providing a regular forum for the presentation and discussion of research in the Institute\'s focus areas.': '全景研究院组织的学术研讨会，为展示和讨论研究院重点领域研究提供常设论坛。',
