    'English (primary)': '英文为主',
    'Propose a Speaker': '推荐演讲者',
    'Panorama Research Seminar Series': '全景研究研讨会系列',
    'The Panorama Research Seminar Series is a planned program of regular academic seminars providing a forum for researchers to present work in the Institute\'s focus areas. The seminar series is designed to support scholarly exchange, introduce new research to the community, and foster connections among researchers working on related questions.': '全景研究研讨会系列是计划中的常设学术研讨项目，为研究人员展示研究院重点领域成果提供论坛。该系列旨在支持学术交流，向共同体介绍新研究，并促进相关议题研究者之间的联系。',
    'Seminars will feature invited presentations from scholars affiliated with the Institute and from external researchers. Each session will include a presentation followed by a structured discussion period. Seminars will be held in hybrid format, accessible to remote participants globally.': '研讨会将邀请研究院相关学者和外部研究人员报告。每场包括报告和结构化讨论环节。研讨会将采用混合形式，全球远程参与者均可参加。',
    'Program Status': '项目状态',
    'The Panorama Research Seminar Series is planned to launch in 2026. Announcements for the inaugural session will be made through the Institute\'s website and mailing list. Register your interest to receive notifications when the program is announced.': '全景研究研讨会系列计划于 2026 年启动。首场活动公告将通过研究院网站和邮件列表发布。登记意向后可在项目公布时接收通知。',
    'Planned Seminar Themes': '计划研讨主题',
