    'Peer review reform: evidence and alternatives': '同行评审改革：证据与替代方案',
    'Youth digital environments: research and policy': '青年数字环境：研究与政策',
    'Five-Year Plan and higher education: policy implications': '五年规划与高等教育：政策影响',
    'Capacity-building training programs organized by Panorama Research Institute for researchers, journal editors, and scholarly practitioners in the Institute\'s focus areas.': '全景研究院为研究人员、期刊编辑和学术实践者组织的能力建设培训项目，聚焦研究院重点领域。',
    'Panorama Research Institute plans to develop a program of training workshops and capacity-building programs for researchers, journal editors, and other scholarly practitioners. Training programs are designed to translate research insights from the Institute\'s projects into practical skills and knowledge that participants can apply directly in their work.': '全景研究院计划发展培训工作坊和能力建设项目，面向研究人员、期刊编辑和其他学术实践者。培训项目旨在将研究院项目中的研究洞见转化为参与者可直接应用于工作的实践技能和知识。',
    'Journal Editors': '期刊编辑',
    'Editorial standards and processes': '编辑标准与流程',
    'Peer review management': '同行评审管理',
    'Publication ethics and COPE guidelines': '出版伦理与 COPE 指南',
    'Managing author relationships': '作者关系管理',
    'Handling retractions and corrections': '撤稿与更正处理',
