    'Preferred; APC support subject to availability': '优先开放获取；APC 支持视资源情况而定',
    'Institutional affiliation, editorial guidance, publisher engagement': '机构隶属、编辑指导、出版社对接',
    'Submit a proposal to edit an academic volume to be published in association with Panorama Research Institute. The Institute supports volume editors with institutional affiliation, editorial guidance, and publisher engagement.': '提交主编学术文集提案，与全景研究院合作出版。研究院为文集主编提供机构隶属、编辑指导和出版社对接支持。',
    'Researchers wishing to edit an academic volume in association with Panorama Research Institute are invited to submit a proposal. The Institute considers proposals that fall within its designated research areas and that represent a coherent and significant scholarly contribution.': '有意与全景研究院合作主编学术文集的研究人员可提交提案。研究院将考虑符合指定研究领域、并具有连贯且重要学术贡献的提案。',
    'Working title and 300-word synopsis of the volume\'s scope and significance.': '文集暂定标题，以及 300 词范围与意义概要。',
    'Primary and secondary readership for the volume.': '文集的主要和次要读者群。',
    'Provisional chapter list with working titles and 50-word abstracts.': '含暂定标题和 50 词摘要的临时章节清单。',
    'Target publisher or publishers, with any existing discussions noted.': '目标出版社，并说明已有沟通情况。',
    'Proposed call for chapters, submission, and publication timeline.': '拟定章节征集、投稿和出版时间表。',
    'Proposed open access model and any existing APC funding.': '拟定开放获取模式及已有 APC 经费。',
    'Lead Editor Name': '主编姓名',
    'Working Title': '暂定标题',
    'Volume Proposal (see guidelines above)': '文集提案（见上方指南）',
    'Submit Volume Proposal': '提交文集提案',
    'Submit a proposal to co-organize a conference, seminar, workshop, or training program with Panorama Research Institute. The Institute welcomes event cooperation with academic institutions and scholarly organizations.': '提交与全景研究院联合组织会议、研讨会、工作坊或培训项目的提案。研究院欢迎与学术机构和学术组织开展活动合作。',
    'Event Types': '活动类型',
    'International academic gathering': '国际学术集会',
    'Single-session scholarly presentation': '单场学术报告',
    'Participatory research development': '参与式研究发展',
    'Training': '培训',
    'Roundtable': '圆桌会议',
    'Closed expert discussion': '闭门专家讨论',
    'Events Overview': '活动概览',
    'Panorama Research Institute welcomes proposals for co-organized academic events from universities, research institutes, scholarly associations, and individual researchers. Co-organized events benefit from the Institute\'s institutional affiliation, editorial support, and scholarly network. The Institute is particularly interested in events that align with its research areas and contribute to scholarly community development.': '全景研究院欢迎大学、研究机构、学术协会和个体研究人员提交联合组织学术活动的提案。联合活动可获得研究院机构隶属、编辑支持和学术网络资源。研究院特别关注与本院研究领域契合并有助于学术共同体发展的活动。',
    'What the Institute Offers Co-organizers': '研究院为联合组织方提供',
    'Institutional co-branding as a Panorama Research Institute event': '作为全景研究院活动的机构联合品牌支持',
    'Support in identifying invited speakers from the Institute\'s scholarly network': '协助从研究院学术网络中确定受邀演讲者',
    'Publication of event proceedings or summaries in the Institute\'s repository': '在研究院资源库发布活动论文集或摘要',
    'Promotion through the Institute\'s communication channels': '通过研究院传播渠道推广',
    'Event coordination support and guidance from the Academic Events Unit': '学术活动事务部提供活动协调支持和指导',
    'Proposed Event Type': '拟议活动类型',
    'Proposed Date / Period': '拟议日期 / 时段',
    'Expected Participants': '预计参与者',
    'Event Description and Cooperation Proposal (up to 600 words)': '活动说明与合作提案（不超过 600 词）',
    'Panorama Research Institute engages with scholars, research teams, and institutions through a range of formal and informal collaboration arrangements. All collaboration is subject to the Institute\'s governance framework and research ethics principles.': '全景研究院通过多种正式和非正式合作安排与学者、研究团队和机构开展合作。所有合作均须遵守研究院治理框架和研究伦理原则。',
    'Submit a collaboration inquiry or proposal using the form. The Institute reviews all submissions and responds within 10 working days.': '请使用表格提交合作咨询或提案。研究院会评审所有提交内容，并在 10 个工作日内回复。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is open to formal institutional cooperation agreements with universities, research institutions, publishers, and scholarly organizations sharing its commitment to independent research and open scholarly communication.': '全景研究院欢迎与同样致力于独立研究和开放学术传播的大学、研究机构、出版社和学术组织建立正式机构合作协议。',
    'Instrument': '协议工具',
    'Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) or Cooperation Agreement': '谅解备忘录（MoU）或合作协议',
    'Typically 2–5 years, renewable': '通常 2–5 年，可续期',
    'Execution': '签署执行',
    'By Panorama Scholarly Group on behalf of the Institute': '由全景学术集团代表研究院签署',
    'Target Partners': '目标伙伴',
    'Universities, research institutes, publishers, scholarly organizations': '大学、研究机构、出版社、学术组织',
    'Submit Inquiry': '提交咨询',
    'Panorama Research Institute is open to establishing formal institutional cooperation relationships with universities, research institutes, academic publishers, and scholarly organizations whose work aligns with the Institute\'s mission and research areas. Institutional cooperation agreements provide a framework for sustained collaboration on research, publications, events, and scholar exchange.': '全景研究院欢迎与工作方向符合研究院使命和研究领域的大学、研究机构、学术出版社和学术组织建立正式机构合作关系。机构合作协议为研究、出版、活动和学者交流方面的持续合作提供框架。',
    'Formal cooperation is typically documented through a Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) or Cooperation Agreement. As the Institute does not hold independent legal personality, such instruments are executed by Panorama Scholarly Group on behalf of the Institute. The terms, scope, and duration of cooperation are negotiated individually with each partner institution.': '正式合作通常通过谅解备忘录（MoU）或合作协议记录。由于研究院不具备独立法人资格，此类文件由全景学术集团代表研究院签署。合作条款、范围和期限将与每个伙伴机构分别协商。',
    'Typical Cooperation Activities': '典型合作活动',
    'Joint Research': '联合研究',
    'Co-designing and conducting research projects of mutual scholarly interest.': '共同设计并开展双方具有学术兴趣的研究项目。',
    'Scholar Exchange': '学者交流',
    'Facilitating visiting scholar placements and fellowship opportunities between institutions.': '促进机构之间的访问学者安排和研究员机会。',
    'Joint Publications': '联合出版',
    'Co-publishing research reports, working papers, or edited volumes.': '联合出版研究报告、工作论文或主编文集。',
