    'Proposals must fall within the Institute\'s designated research areas. They will be assessed on scholarly quality, feasibility, fit with the Institute\'s research program, and the proposer\'s qualifications and track record.': '提案必须属于研究院指定研究领域。评审将依据学术质量、可行性、与研究院研究项目的契合度，以及提案人的资历和过往记录进行。',
