    'Research on artificial intelligence, technology governance, digital transformation, academic infrastructure, and social impact.': '研究人工智慧、技術治理、數位轉型、學術基礎設施和社會影響。',
    'Research on education policy, higher education, learning science, academic development, and institutional change.': '研究教育政策、高等教育、學習科學、學術發展和制度變遷。',
