    'Annual reports include a message from the Institute Director, a summary of research progress by center, a full list of publications and events, governance and policy disclosures, and an institutional outlook for the coming year. Reports are published open access and are permanently available in the Institute\'s repository.': '年度報告包括院長致辭、各研究中心研究進展摘要、出版成果與活動完整清單、治理和政策揭露，以及下一年度機構展望。報告以開放取用形式發布，並永久保存在研究院資源庫中。',
