    'Panorama Research Institute plans to develop a program of edited academic volumes, published in association with partner academic publishers. Edited volumes bring together original contributions from multiple scholars on themes that are central to the Institute\'s research program.': '全景研究院計劃發展主編學術文集項目，並與合作學術出版社聯合出版。主編文集圍繞研究院研究項目的核心主題，匯集多位學者的原創貢獻。',
    'Volume proposals may be submitted by researchers with a clear thematic vision and the capacity to lead an editorial process. The Institute provides institutional affiliation, editorial support, and assistance in identifying contributors and a suitable publisher. Volume editors receive support from the Publications Unit throughout the production process.': '具備明確主題構想並有能力主持編輯流程的研究人員可提交文集提案。研究院提供機構隸屬、編輯支持，並協助尋找作者和合適出版社。文集主編將在整個出版流程中獲得學術出版事務部支持。',
    'Calls for chapters for active edited volume projects are published on the Institute\'s events and calls pages. Chapter contributors do not need to be affiliated with the Institute, but their contributions must fall within the scope of the volume and meet the Institute\'s publication standards.': '正在進行的主編文集項目會在研究院活動與徵集頁面發布章節徵集。章節作者不必隸屬於研究院，但其稿件必須符合文集範圍並達到研究院出版標準。',
    'The Institute\'s edited volume program is currently in its planning stage. The first edited volume is expected to be announced in 2026. Researchers wishing to propose a volume may do so at any time using the proposal form.': '研究院主編文集項目目前處於規劃階段。首部主編文集預計於 2026 年公布。有意提出文集提案的研究人員可隨時通過提案表格提交。',
    'Editorial guidelines, scholarly communication standards, and publication ethics frameworks developed and published by Panorama Research Institute for use by journals, publishers, and academic institutions.': '全景研究院制定並發布的編輯指南、學術傳播標準和出版倫理框架，供期刊、出版社和學術機構使用。',
    'Panorama Research Institute develops and publishes practical guidelines and standards documents alongside its research reports and working papers. These documents are produced by the Scholarly Publishing Standards Project and related initiatives, and are intended for use by journal editors, publishers, institutions, and researchers.': '全景研究院在發布研究報告和工作論文的同時，也制定並發布實踐性指南和標準文件。這些文件由學術出版標準項目及相關計劃形成，面向期刊編輯、出版社、機構和研究人員使用。',
