    'Full-length research reports presenting substantial original findings from Panorama Research Institute\'s research projects. Research reports represent the Institute\'s primary long-form publication format.': '完整研究報告呈現全景研究院研究項目的重要原創發現，是研究院主要的長篇出版形式。',
