    'English (primary); Chinese (selected)': '英文為主；部分中文',
    'Propose a Project': '提出項目提案',
    'Research reports are Panorama Research Institute\'s primary format for presenting substantial research findings. They are full-length academic documents presenting original research, systematic analysis, and evidence-based conclusions. Research reports go through both internal review and external peer review before publication.': '研究報告是全景研究院呈現重要研究發現的主要形式。它們是完整的學術文件，呈現原創研究、系統分析和基於證據的結論。研究報告在出版前需經過內部評審和外部同儕評審。',
    'All research reports are published under open access terms and are freely available for download. Each report receives a DOI for permanent citation and discoverability. Reports are typically associated with one of the Institute\'s active research projects.': '所有研究報告均以開放取用方式發布，可免費下載。每份報告均獲得 DOI，以便永久引用和發現。報告通常關聯研究院正在進行的研究項目。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is currently in its foundational phase. Research reports from active projects are currently in preparation and will be published as they are completed. Please check back or see the': '全景研究院目前處於基礎建設階段。當前項目的研究報告正在籌備中，將在完成後陸續發布。請稍後查看，或參閱',
    'publications overview': '出版成果概覽',
    'for the most recent outputs.': '了解最新成果。',
    'Working papers presenting preliminary research findings, theoretical arguments, and ongoing scholarly work from researchers affiliated with Panorama Research Institute.': '工作論文呈現全景研究院相關研究人員的初步研究發現、理論論證和進行中的學術工作。',
