    'Become a Fellow': '成為研究員',
    'Working papers are a key publication format for Panorama Research Institute, enabling rapid dissemination of research findings, theoretical contributions, and scholarly arguments before or alongside the formal peer review process. Working papers may present preliminary findings, theoretical frameworks, systematic literature reviews, or commentary on emerging developments in the Institute\'s research areas.': '工作論文是全景研究院的重要出版形式，使研究發現、理論貢獻和學術論證能夠在正式同儕評審之前或同時快速傳播。工作論文可呈現初步發現、理論框架、系統文獻綜述，或對研究院相關領域新發展作出評論。',
    'All working papers are published under open access terms and receive DOIs. The Institute\'s working paper series is open to submissions from affiliated research fellows, visiting scholars, and invited contributors working within the Institute\'s research areas.': '所有工作論文均以開放取用方式發布並獲得 DOI。研究院工作論文系列接受隸屬研究員、訪問學者以及在研究院研究領域內工作的受邀貢獻者投稿。',
