    'Panorama Research Institute was established in 2026 and is currently in its foundational phase. No events have yet been completed and archived. This page will be updated following the Institute\'s inaugural events.': '全景研究院成立於 2026 年，目前處於基礎建設階段。尚無已完成並歸檔的活動。研究院首批活動結束後，本頁面將更新。',
    'Completed events are archived here with records of the event date, program, participants, and any outputs produced — including proceedings, summaries, or recordings where available.': '已完成活動將在此歸檔，並記錄活動日期、議程、參與者以及形成的成果，包括可提供的會議論文集、摘要或錄音錄影。',
    'Open calls for chapter submissions for edited volumes published in association with Panorama Research Institute. Contribute original research to collaborative scholarly volumes on the Institute\'s research themes.': '全景研究院合作出版主編文集的章節徵集。歡迎圍繞研究院研究主題為合作學術文集提交原創研究。',
    'No calls for chapters are currently open. Panorama Research Institute\'s edited volume program is in its planning stage, with the first volume anticipated to be announced in 2026.': '目前暫無開放的章節徵集。全景研究院主編文集項目處於規劃階段，首部文集預計於 2026 年公布。',
