    'Panorama Research Institute is developing a program of edited academic volumes on themes central to its research program. Edited volumes bring together original chapters from multiple scholars, providing a comprehensive treatment of a research theme that no single author could produce alone.': '全景研究院正在圍繞其研究項目核心主題發展主編學術文集項目。主編文集匯集多位學者的原創章節，對單一作者難以獨立完成的研究主題進行綜合討論。',
    'When a call for chapters is open, chapter contributors do not need to be formally affiliated with the Institute. Submissions must fall within the scope of the volume, meet the Institute\'s publication standards, and be submitted by the stated deadline. Each call includes specific guidance on the expected chapter length, format, review process, and publication timeline.': '開放章節徵集時，章節作者不必正式隸屬於研究院。投稿必須符合文集範圍，達到研究院出版標準，並在規定截止日期前提交。每項徵集都會說明章節預期長度、格式、評審流程和出版時間表。',
