    'The Institute\'s first major conference is planned for 2026. Calls for papers will be issued approximately six months before the event.': '研究院首個大型會議計劃於 2026 年舉行。論文徵稿預計將在活動前約六個月發布。',
    'How Calls Work': '徵集流程',
    'When a call for papers is open, it will be listed here with the event name, submission deadline, format requirements, themes, and submission link. Submissions may be for full papers, extended abstracts, or panel proposals, depending on the event.': '開放論文徵稿時，本頁將列出活動名稱、投稿截止日期、格式要求、主題和提交連結。根據活動類型，投稿可包括全文論文、擴展摘要或專題小組提案。',
    'All submissions are reviewed by the event\'s scientific committee. Accepted papers will be notified and invited to present. Selected presentations from Institute-organized conferences and seminars may be developed into publications in the Institute\'s working paper or other series.': '所有投稿均由活動學術委員會評審。被接受論文的作者將收到通知並受邀報告。研究院主辦會議和研討會中的部分報告可進一步發展為研究院工作論文或其他系列出版成果。',
