    'Panorama Research Institute plans to develop an international conference program centered on the Institute\'s core research themes of scholarly publishing, journal evaluation, academic policy, and emerging digital futures. The first Institute-organized conference is planned for 2026.': '全景研究院計劃發展國際會議項目，圍繞學術出版、期刊評價、學術政策和新興數位未來等核心研究主題展開。研究院首個主辦會議計劃於 2026 年舉行。',
    'Upcoming — Planning Stage': '即將開展——規劃階段',
    'The Institute is in the early planning stage for its inaugural international conference on scholarly communication, academic publishing, and open science. The conference will bring together researchers, editors, publishers, librarians, and policymakers from across the Asia-Pacific region and beyond.': '研究院首屆關於學術傳播、學術出版和開放科學的國際會議處於早期規劃階段。會議將匯集亞太地區及其他地區的研究人員、編輯、出版商、圖書館員和政策制定者。',
