    'Seminars will feature invited presentations from scholars affiliated with the Institute and from external researchers. Each session will include a presentation followed by a structured discussion period. Seminars will be held in hybrid format, accessible to remote participants globally.': '研討會將邀請研究院相關學者和外部研究人員報告。每場包括報告和結構化討論環節。研討會將採用混合形式，全球遠端參與者均可參加。',
