    'Capacity-building training programs organized by Panorama Research Institute for researchers, journal editors, and scholarly practitioners in the Institute\'s focus areas.': '全景研究院為研究人員、期刊編輯和學術實踐者組織的能力建設培訓項目，聚焦研究院重點領域。',
    'Panorama Research Institute plans to develop a program of training workshops and capacity-building programs for researchers, journal editors, and other scholarly practitioners. Training programs are designed to translate research insights from the Institute\'s projects into practical skills and knowledge that participants can apply directly in their work.': '全景研究院計劃發展培訓工作坊和能力建設項目，面向研究人員、期刊編輯和其他學術實踐者。培訓項目旨在將研究院項目中的研究洞見轉化為參與者可直接應用於工作的實踐技能和知識。',
    'Journal Editors': '期刊編輯',
