    'Institutional affiliation, editorial guidance, publisher engagement': '機構隸屬、編輯指導、出版社對接',
    'Submit a proposal to edit an academic volume to be published in association with Panorama Research Institute. The Institute supports volume editors with institutional affiliation, editorial guidance, and publisher engagement.': '提交主編學術文集提案，與全景研究院合作出版。研究院為文集主編提供機構隸屬、編輯指導和出版社對接支持。',
    'Researchers wishing to edit an academic volume in association with Panorama Research Institute are invited to submit a proposal. The Institute considers proposals that fall within its designated research areas and that represent a coherent and significant scholarly contribution.': '有意與全景研究院合作主編學術文集的研究人員可提交提案。研究院將考慮符合指定研究領域、並具有連貫且重要學術貢獻的提案。',
    'Working title and 300-word synopsis of the volume\'s scope and significance.': '文集暫定標題，以及 300 詞範圍與意義概要。',
    'Primary and secondary readership for the volume.': '文集的主要和次要讀者群。',
    'Provisional chapter list with working titles and 50-word abstracts.': '含暫定標題和 50 詞摘要的臨時章節清單。',
