    'Read Online': '線上閱讀',
    'The Charter of Panorama Research Institute is the Institute\'s founding governance document. It establishes the Institute\'s name, mission, structure, research areas, operational principles, and governance framework. The Charter is adopted under the authority of Panorama Scholarly Group and constitutes the primary constitutional document of the Institute.': '《全景研究院章程》是研究院的創始治理文件，確立研究院名稱、使命、結構、研究領域、運行原則和治理框架。章程在全景學術集團授權下通過，是研究院的基本制度文件。',
    'The Charter consists of 20 articles covering the Institute\'s legal status, mission and vision, research areas, organizational structure, governance bodies, research ethics, publication policies, collaboration framework, scholar programs, and amendment procedures. It should be read in conjunction with the Institute\'s subsidiary governance policies.': '章程共 20 條，涵蓋研究院法律地位、使命與願景、研究領域、組織架構、治理機構、研究倫理、出版政策、合作框架、學者計劃和修訂程序。章程應與研究院附屬治理政策一併閱讀。',
