    'In formal instruments: "Panorama Research Institute (an internal research division of Panorama Scholarly Group)"': '正式文件中："Panorama Research Institute (an internal research division of Panorama Scholarly Group)"',
    'Logo Usage': '標誌使用',
    'When using the Institute\'s logo, follow these requirements:': '使用研究院標誌時，請遵守以下要求：',
    'Use only the official logo files available from the Institute\'s Publications Unit': '僅使用研究院學術出版事務部提供的官方標誌文件',
    'Maintain the minimum clear space around the logo (equal to the height of the \'P\' in PANORAMA on all sides)': '保持標誌周圍最小留白（四周均等於 PANORAMA 中字母 P 的高度）',
