    'Data, instruments, additional tables': '資料、工具、附加表格',
    'Brief bio (50–100 words per author)': '簡短作者簡介（每位作者 50–100 詞）',
    'The official template for submitting research project proposals to Panorama Research Institute. Use this template to prepare a complete, correctly structured proposal for submission.': '用於向全景研究院提交研究項目提案的官方範本。請使用此範本準備完整且結構正確的提案。',
